WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.470 --> 00:00:07.380
- I think the most important
distinction between when

2
00:00:07.380 --> 00:00:10.050
to use Gemini app and
when to use Canvas mode

3
00:00:10.050 --> 00:00:11.910
is when you want to collaborate

4
00:00:11.910 --> 00:00:13.860
with the model to create something

5
00:00:13.860 --> 00:00:16.230
that maybe you then wanna export out.

6
00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:18.270
Oftentimes in a chat thread,

7
00:00:18.270 --> 00:00:20.430
it's hard to pinpoint I wanna change

8
00:00:20.430 --> 00:00:22.110
this specific line of the response,

9
00:00:22.110 --> 00:00:26.220
or I want to add something
here after this paragraph.

10
00:00:26.220 --> 00:00:29.010
That can be hard to call
out in a chat thread.

11
00:00:29.010 --> 00:00:31.650
But in Canvas, you can just
highlight certain portions

12
00:00:31.650 --> 00:00:35.190
of the text and have a conversation
with Gemini about that.

13
00:00:35.190 --> 00:00:37.620
And then maybe this is
like writing an email,

14
00:00:37.620 --> 00:00:40.917
edit all of it together, and
then export it out one time.